                    <p>
                    <strong><a href="/">ArturoNet.com</a><strong> powered by Hitler and ISIS. JK NOT TRUE</strong>. Made by <a href="/404">TheOfficialDixionary</a>
                    </p>
                    <p>
                    <a class="icon" href="https://github.com/ArturoGuerra/arturonet">
                        <i class="fa fa-github"></i>
